com.vmware.vcenter.vm.guest.networking

Interface InterfacesTypes

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Interfaces
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    InterfacesStub

    public interface InterfacesTypes
    The Interfaces interface provides methods for retrieving guest operating system network interface information. This interface was added in vSphere API 7.0.0.0.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  InterfacesTypes.Info
      The Info class describes a virtual network adapter configured in the guest operating system.
      static class  InterfacesTypes.IpAddressInfo
      The IpAddressInfo class describes a specific IP Address.
      static class  InterfacesTypes.IpAddressOrigin
      The IpAddressOrigin enumeration class specifies how an IP address was obtained for an interface.
      static class  InterfacesTypes.IpAddressStatus
      The IpAddressStatus enumeration class defines the present status of an address on an interface.
      static class  InterfacesTypes.IpConfigInfo
      The IpConfigInfo class describes the protocol version independent address reporting data object for network interfaces.
